Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:363810,365810}That one serve decided it all.{NOTE:あの一級で。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.44,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:376910,378440}{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:26.56,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:384960,386560}Chance ball!{NOTE:チャンスボール！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:28.01,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{TIME:386560,388010}Leave it to me!{NOTE:任せて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:32.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:390510,392190}Attack!{NOTE:アタック！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:45.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:402860,405080}We did it! We did it!{NOTE:やったわ！やったわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:47.53,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:405080,407530}– Midori!\N– Ayuhara-san!{NOTE:—みどり！\\N—鮎原さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:56.70,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:414990,416700}– Ayuhara.\N– Sir.{NOTE:—鮎原。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.79,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:418040,419790}Look at that bird over there.{NOTE:あそこに鳥がいるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.53,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:422730,424530}Do you think I can hit that bird?{NOTE:あの鳥に当てられると思うか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:05.80,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:424530,425800}Huh?{NOTE:は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:09.28,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:425800,429280}Why don't we make a bet if I can hit it or not?{NOTE:掛けてみないか？僕は当たるの方に掛ける。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.50,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:429280,430500}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:18.06,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:435680,438060}Haha, looks like I lost.{NOTE:ハハハ、いかん、いかん。僕の負けだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:24.30,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:440930,444300}Ayuhara. That ball was a bet too, wasn't it?{NOTE:鮎原。あのボールは掛けだったな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:28.82,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:444300,448820}It was a brilliant serve that had to be served very precisely and from the right angle.{NOTE:角度とポイントを決め狙った(こうそう)正確に打った素晴らしいボールだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:33.12,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:448820,453120}But it was extremely difficult to get right, which made it a desperate gamble.{NOTE:しかし、あの状況でしか打てない。一か八かの掛けだったな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:38.17,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:454570,458170}We don't know if you'll be able to pull it off ever again.{NOTE:もう一度あのボールを打てる時が来るかどうか分からない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:40.22,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:458170,460220}It's very possible that you might not.{NOTE:二度と打てないボールかもしれない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:42.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:460220,462550}I know.{NOTE:そう何です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:462550,464720}I know that I probably couldn't.{NOTE:もう二度と打てないでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:46.42,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:464720,466420}Look, betting is necessary.{NOTE:掛けることは必要だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:49.35,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:466420,469350}That bet led you to victory, after all.{NOTE:あの一級に掛けて、勝負に勝った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:51.30,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:469350,471300}But a bet is still a bet.{NOTE:しかし、掛けは掛けだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:54.30,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:471300,474300}When you fail, there are no second chances.{NOTE:一度だけの掛けに失敗したら、もう二度目はない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.75,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:474300,475750}{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:01.81,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:478710,481810}It's the same with that bird. I can't try hitting it anymore.{NOTE:あの鳥にXXXを当てることはもう出来ない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:07.05,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:484310,487050}Fukuoka's adding offense to their excellent defense.{NOTE:あの固い守りの上に、攻撃力。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:10.05,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:487050,490050}What kind of team will they become?{NOTE:福岡中学どんなチームに成ってくるんだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.28,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:490050,491280}I will admit that it is scary.{NOTE:確かに怖い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:13.40,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:491280,493400}But it's also kind of exciting, isn't it?{NOTE:しかし、楽しみじゃないか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.65,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:493400,495650}What team will they become?{NOTE:どんなチームに成ってくるんかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:36.91,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:513460,516910}Professor, our spring victory doesn't matter anymore.{NOTE:先生、春の大会の勝ち負けはもう関係ありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:42.73,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:516910,522730}Since Fukuoka is working to become a better team, we'll do the same.{NOTE:福岡中もは新しい力。此方も新しい力で精一杯戦うだけです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:58.19,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:525750,538190}One-two! One-two!\NOne-two! One-two!{NOTE:一二。一二。一二。一二。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:09:01.94,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:538190,541940}– Captain sure is motivated!\N– She looks scary.{NOTE:—キャプテンすごいファイトで。\\N—怖いみたいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:09.17,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:546570,549170}Hey!{NOTE:おい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:14.91,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:551840,554910}You idiot! Skirt chasers have no business playing football.{NOTE:バカやろ。女の子とは遊びたい奴はサッカーなんか止めちまえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:18.21,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:554910,558210}– Sorry, I let my guard down. Captain.\N– What is it?{NOTE:—あ、びっくりした。だけどさ、キャプテン…\\N—なんだよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:22.59,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:558210,562590}Those aren't just some girls. They're the best volleyballers in Japan.{NOTE:彼女達は女の子なんかじゃないんだぜ。日本一のバレー部の戦士だぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:24.64,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:562590,564640}Yeah. They're Tōkai's witches.{NOTE:そうだよ。東海の魔女たちだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.21,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:564640,566210}That's some impressive training.{NOTE:すごい練習だろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:28.71,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:566210,568710}They'll win the next championship for sure.{NOTE:や、今度も全国優勝間違いないね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:32.21,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:568710,572210}Yeah, I think the s—\NYou idiots, get back to work!{NOTE:え、そ、そうだは-バカやろ！そんなこと言ってんじゃないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.96,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:572210,574960}Let's go!{NOTE:さ、行くぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:37.45,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:575860,577450}Shut up already!{NOTE:あ、煩いな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:40.10,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:577450,580100}You don't like it? Well, it's music to my ears.{NOTE:そうかな？俺には気持ちのいい音だがな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:43.27,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:580100,583270}The sweet sound of a new gym for our champion team.{NOTE:全国大会に優勝したバレー部の体育館ができるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:45.27,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:583270,585270}It's great accompaniment to our practice.{NOTE:俺たちにも素敵な伴奏じゃないか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.82,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:585270,586820}Now, let's continue.{NOTE:さ！XXXやろうぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:48.55,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:586820,588550}{NOTE:おう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:01.17,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:599720,601170}– Shoot!\N– Got it!{NOTE:—シュート！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.91,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:625560,627910}All right, listen up!{NOTE:はい。止めれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:630400,632930}Time for light passes, so get ready.{NOTE:さ。軽くパスからよ。皆よいして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.37,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:633670,635370}Captain, I've had enough.{NOTE:キャプテン、もうダメ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:37.05,Default,Ikezaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:635370,637050}Me too!{NOTE:あ、あたしも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:40.75,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{TIME:637050,640750}Please let us rest for a moment, captain.{NOTE:あ、ちょっと休ませて、お願いキャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:42.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:640750,642450}Oh, stand up. Come on!{NOTE:立って。さ、立って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:45.15,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:642450,645150}Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:48.40,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:645150,648400}All of our rivals have already started training for the autumn matches.{NOTE:秋の大会を目指して、日本中のバレー部がスタートおしたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:50.40,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:648400,650400}Are you okay with being behind the curve?{NOTE:あたしたちだけは遅れていいの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:56.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:654190,656590}From now on, we will train every day.{NOTE:これから練習は一日。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:57.49,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:656590,657490}Every day!{NOTE:一日。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.49,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:657490,659490}And each day I'll make it a little harder.{NOTE:段々厳しくして行くつもりよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:02.17,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:659490,662170}– Eh?\N– Harder?{NOTE:へ？厳しい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:04.20,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:662170,664200}More than it already is?{NOTE:これ以上？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:10.78,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:669580,670780}Hey.{NOTE:おい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:11.93,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:670780,671930}What's wrong?{NOTE:どうした？ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:15.06,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:671930,675060}Ah, professor!{NOTE:あ、先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:18.66,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:675060,678660}Hahaha. Seems like some of you aren't taking too kindly to captain Ayuhara's true colors.{NOTE:ハハハ。鮎原の発破にもう目を開けたものがいるんだな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:20.96,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:678660,680960}If you have a problem with it, then drop out now.{NOTE:そんなものはすぐ止めてしまえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:23.66,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:680960,683660}Members who can't obey their captain are of no use to the team.{NOTE:キャプテンについていけないものはチームにでも仕方はない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.16,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:683660,685160}So save everyone's time and quit.{NOTE:すぐ止めるんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.63,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:685160,687630}I'm sorry, but I won't step in.{NOTE:残念だが、僕はコートに入られないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:30.43,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:687630,690430}What happens on the court is up to our captain.{NOTE:コートに入ったら、キャプテンのXXXしたがうべきだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.93,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:690430,691930}– Ah.\N– Got it?{NOTE:—あ。\\N—そうだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:34.21,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:691930,694210}Well? Do you understand or not?{NOTE:どうしたんだ？分かったのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.83,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:694210,695830}– We understand.\N– Very well.{NOTE:—はい。\\N—よし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:37.38,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:695830,697380}All right then! Ayuhara, resume!{NOTE:鮎原。始めろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:697380,699630}Yes sir! Let's start with passes then.{NOTE:はい。では、パスからよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.68,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:699630,701680}– All right.\N– Okay, okay.{NOTE:—よし。\\N—やろう、やろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:44.86,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:703160,704860}– Heave-ho.\N– Here we go.{NOTE:—よいっしょ。\\N—はい。}
Comment: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:14.73,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:734733,734733}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:27.41,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:745660,747410}It'll be finished soon.{NOTE:もうすぐ完全ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:31.46,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:747410,751460}Yeah. It's practically done already. All but of a few finishing touches.{NOTE:そう。殆んど出来てんだよ。後はもう仕上げだけらしいわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:35.54,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:751460,755540}It'll be done before summer vacation's over. It's a wonder they built it so quickly.{NOTE:夏休みまでに完成させたいって突貫工事だったもんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:39.00,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:755540,759000}I want to practice on the court already.{NOTE:早くのコートで練習したいわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:41.38,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:759000,761380}Hey, girls.{NOTE:ね、皆。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:43.17,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:761380,763170}– What's up?\N– Something happened?{NOTE:—なによ？\\N—どうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:46.14,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:763170,766140}Captain said to go ahead by ourselves.{NOTE:キャプテンは「先に帰って」って言って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:47.93,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:766140,767930}What? She won't be joining us?{NOTE:あら？なんかあるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:51.72,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:767930,771720}She's discussing our summer schedule with professor Hongou.{NOTE:本郷先生と夏休みのスケジュールの打ち合わせなんだって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:55.23,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:771720,775230}Really? I wanted to talk to her about that myself.{NOTE:そう？あたしもちょっと放したいことがあったのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:56.06,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:775230,776060}What for?{NOTE:何なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:59.57,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:776060,779570}It's just… I have my own plans for summer vacation.{NOTE:実は、あたしにも夏休みの計画があるのよ。それで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:01.61,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:779570,781610}Oh? What kind of plans?{NOTE:へ？どんな計画よ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:04.95,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:781610,784950}Well, I wanted to consult it with the our captain first.{NOTE:ん、キャプテンに相談してからって思ってたんだけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:08.12,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{TIME:784950,788120}Come on, spill it. Don't be such a tease.{NOTE:XXX。焦らさないでよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:10.19,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:788120,790190}– Yeah.\N– All right.{NOTE:—ね。\\N—そうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:13.66,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:790190,793660}Well… I guess it's okay to decide it ourselves and surprise her later.{NOTE:あたしたちに先に決めて、キャプテンを驚かす物いいわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:16.21,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:793660,796210}Are you all free now? I'd like to invite you over.{NOTE:ね、皆。これから一緒に家に来てくれる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:17.83,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:796210,797830}I have a wonderful idea.{NOTE:素敵な計画なんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:23.13,Default,Hayakawa's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:800550,803130}Well… I think it's okay.{NOTE:ま、そう言う話ならいいんだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.76,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:803130,805760}Yay!{NOTE:わ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:29.47,Default,Hayakawa's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:805760,809470}All of you can use it however you like.{NOTE:君たち皆の良い的に、好きなように使っているよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:31.43,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:809470,811430}Thank you, papa.{NOTE:有難う、パパ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:33.33,Default,Hayakawa's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:811430,813330}I wouldn't allow it if it was just on Midori's whim…{NOTE:みどりの我侭なら許さんが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:36.35,Default,Hayakawa's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:813330,816350}…but I'll be happy to open our holiday house in Karuizawa for your club.{NOTE:…バレー部のためなら喜んで軽井沢の別荘を提供するよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.27,Default,Hayakawa's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:816350,818270}You can use it during the summer vacation.{NOTE:夏休み中使っていい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.98,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:818270,819980}Yay!{NOTE:わ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:43.32,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:819980,823320}Girls, let's form a plan together, okay?{NOTE:ね、ね。皆でこれから色々と計画を立ててみない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:46.61,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:823320,826610}Yeah. Let's decide where to start first.{NOTE:そうね。えと、先ず、何から決めようか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:49.37,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:826610,829370}– Let's see…\N– Hahahaha.{NOTE:—えと、ね。\\N—ハハハハ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:52.37,Default,Hayakawa's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:829370,832370}I will cover any necessary expenses.{NOTE:必要な費用が私はバレー部に寄付さしていただく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:56.00,Default,Hayakawa's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:832370,836000}Have a good time, girls. Excuse me.{NOTE:な、皆で素晴らしい夏休みをXしなさい。じゃね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:57.96,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:836000,837960}Wah.{NOTE:わ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.42,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:837960,839420}Thank you very much.{NOTE:有難うございました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.59,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:839420,841590}– First of all: food.\N– Do we cook for ourselves?{NOTE:—先ず食べることね。\\N—自炊すんの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:04.13,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:841590,844130}Of course we do. What do you think?{NOTE:そうよ。そんなこと決まってるじゃないの？何あってん—}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:08.38,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:844130,848380}– Then we need to take turns!\N– I've never been there. Say, what is Karuizawa like?{NOTE:—じゃ、交番決めなきゃ。\\N—ね、軽井沢へ行ったことないんだけど、どんな所なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.38,0:14:10.64,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{TIME:848380,850640}Karuizawa is all about tennis.{NOTE:軽井沢って言えば、テニスよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.26,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:850640,852260}Wait, you've been there?{NOTE:軽井沢へ行ったことあるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:14.97,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{TIME:852260,854970}Nope. But it's basic knowledge.{NOTE:いいえ、ないわよ。でも、それぐらい常識で。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:18.02,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:854970,858020}Doesn't it have horses too? I've seen some in the photos, right, Midori-san?{NOTE:馬がいるんでしょう。写真で見たら、ね、みどりさん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:21.06,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:858020,861060}Horses? I didn't know about this.{NOTE:馬？すごい。いっぺんのXXXと思ってたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:23.32,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:861060,863320}Horses and tennis are nice, but we can't forget about vol—{NOTE:馬もテニスもいいけど、バレーを忘れちゃ—}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.99,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:863320,864990}Yeah. That's the most important.{NOTE:そうよ。それは一番大切よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:28.07,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{TIME:864990,868070}But it'll only take up three hours of our afternoon.{NOTE:午前十二時間午後三時間てことじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:30.49,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:868070,870490}We'll make a campfire at night.{NOTE:夜あき、キャンプファイアーよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:33.45,Default,Ikezaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:870490,873450}I bet the stars there are pretty.{NOTE:星が綺麗だろうな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:37.71,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{TIME:873450,877710}You can fish there too, right? I'll whip us up some tasty fish.{NOTE:そうだ。ね、釣りができるんでしょう？皆立派魚XXXにしてさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:39.87,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:877710,879870}Tasty fish would be good after volleyball.{NOTE:魚でバレー休憩のもいいわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:42.04,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:879870,882040}The cycling routes must be great too.{NOTE:サイクリングも素敵よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:43.59,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:882040,883590}Hey, hey, do they have a pool?{NOTE:ねね、パールないの？プール。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:48.80,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:883590,888800}We can't do all of this in a single day. We need to come up with a plan for the whole week.{NOTE:一日に何もかも出来ないんだからさ。先ず一週間ぐらいのスケジュールを立てる見ることよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:53.64,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:888800,893640}– Don't you think?\N– Yeah. Wait a moment. I will write it down.{NOTE:—ね？—そうよ。そうよう。\\N—そうよ。先ずこれからよちょっと待ってね。今書くから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:56.14,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:893640,896140}We'll start with the departure.{NOTE:え、て、一番先はさ、出発、出発。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:01.27,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:899270,901270}{NOTE:—それ！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:906190,907190}{NOTE:ほら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:16.99,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:911740,916990}Oyoshi, what was that? You didn't even accept two serves. Come on, stand up!{NOTE:おヨシ。どうしたのよ？未だ二球も受けてないの。ほら、立って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:19.87,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:918120,919870}– Next!\N– That's me!{NOTE:—次！\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:21.67,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:919870,921670}Our captain is on fire today.{NOTE:キャプテン、気合が入ってるわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:23.67,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:921670,923670}– Here I go.\N– Bring it on.{NOTE:—行くわよ。\\N—どんどん来い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:36.43,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:933900,936430}Oyoshi, are you okay?{NOTE:おヨシ。足大丈夫？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.63,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{TIME:936430,937630}I'm okay.{NOTE:大丈夫。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:40.68,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{TIME:937630,940680}I feel better when I think about going to Karuizawa.{NOTE:軽井沢のこと思えば、これぐらい軽い、軽い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:56.95,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:953490,956950}Hey, are you going to tell our captain about Karuizawa after the training?{NOTE:ね、軽井沢のこと。練習が終わったから、キャプテンに話する？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:02.54,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:958910,962540}Because I'm starting to wonder if that's a good idea. Especially when she's so focused on practice.{NOTE:大丈夫かしら？あんなにかっかしてる時に夏休みの話任してさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:07.13,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:965000,967130}I'll tell her after the briefing.{NOTE:XXX聞いてから話すのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:11.76,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:967130,971760}And it's not like we won't be practicing in Karuizawa, so she should be happy.{NOTE:キャプテンだって、軽井沢でゆっくり練習出来るんだから喜ぶわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:13.18,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:971760,973180}You're right.{NOTE:そうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:21.14,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:978850,981140}That's it for today.{NOTE:今日はここまで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:25.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:981140,985520}Gather around, girls. I'd like to announce our schedule.{NOTE:さ、皆集まって。スケジュールについて話があるから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:29.32,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:985520,989320}The gym will be finished the next week and we'll be finally able to start using it.{NOTE:新しい体育館が完全して、来週から使えるようになったの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:989320,991280}We'll be able to practice more than ever.{NOTE:今まで以上に練習できるわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:36.03,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:991280,996030}Summer vacation starts next week. We'll practice every day in the new gym till the district qualifiers.{NOTE:来週から夏休みになるし。地区予選まで新しい体育館で毎日もう練習よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:37.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:996030,997450}Got it?{NOTE:いいわね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:38.83,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:997450,998830}Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:42.29,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1000830,1002290}In the new gym?{NOTE:体育館で？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:43.29,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1002290,1003290}{NOTE:聞いたことある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:46.46,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003290,1006460}Practice will start at 8 o'clock in the morning.{NOTE:練習時間は朝八時に集合。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:47.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006460,1007790}What's wrong?{NOTE:どうかしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:49.84,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007790,1009840}During the vacation… every day?{NOTE:夏休み中毎日？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:52.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009840,1012420}Yep. Is something the matter?{NOTE:そうよ。それがどうかしたわ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:54.13,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012420,1014130}Bu-But…{NOTE:で、でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.22,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014130,1015220}But what?{NOTE:でも何なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:58.47,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015220,1018470}We kind of have plans, right?{NOTE:いいや、夏休みの計画があるさ。ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:00.60,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018470,1020600}Yeah. It's vacation after all.{NOTE:そうよ。夏休みなんか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.60,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020600,1022600}Please cancel these plans.{NOTE:そんな計画は皆取り消して。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:07.23,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022600,1027230}Us volleyball players have All-Japan championships in the September.{NOTE:バレー部員だったら、九月には全日本の選手権大会があるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:10.36,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027230,1030360}It's only natural that we train every day during the summer.{NOTE:夏休みだって毎日練習するのが当然のことよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:13.65,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1030360,1033650}– But, but…\N– This is absurd.{NOTE:—で、でも。\\N—でも。ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:19.95,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036990,1039950}Midori, Kakko, you understand, right?{NOTE:みどり、カッコ。あなたたちなら、分かってくれるわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:23.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042200,1043580}You too?{NOTE:あなったちまで？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.83,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043580,1045830}Actually, I wanted to talk to you about it before.{NOTE:実は、あたしのXXことなんだけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:29.71,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045830,1049710}All of us were planning to spend the vacation in Karuizawa.{NOTE:夏休みには皆で軽井沢に計画を立てていたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:31.00,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049710,1051000}Karuizawa?{NOTE:軽井沢？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:35.22,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051000,1055220}Yep, papa has agreed to open a\hvacation house in Karuizawa for us.{NOTE:うん。パパが軽井沢の別荘をバレー部に開けてくれるって言うし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:37.84,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055220,1057840}We wanted to go camping and have some fun.{NOTE:皆で合宿して、夏休みの楽しくすごそうと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:41.18,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057840,1061180}So, we all decided to suspend the practice.{NOTE:もちろん、バレーの練習を中止にしてよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:43.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061180,1063640}I'm sorry, but you'll have to cancel that trip.{NOTE:せっかくだけど、その計画も中止ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:46.77,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063640,1066770}We've just received a brand new gym.{NOTE:あたしたちにはバレー部専用の新しい体育館が出来たのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:49.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066770,1069310}We should use it.{NOTE:毎日そこで練習すればいいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:51.86,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069310,1071860}Look, volleyball is important to us, too.{NOTE:確かに、あたしたちにとって、バレーは大切よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:54.03,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071860,1074030}And nobody's objecting to the training.{NOTE:誰も「練習いいやだ」とは言ってないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:57.95,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074030,1077950}But we should take a break during the summer, don't you think?{NOTE:でも、せめて夏休みにはすこしぐらしXXてもいいじゃないかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.66,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077950,1080660}It's not necessary to be so strict.{NOTE:そこまで厳しくしなくても。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:03.20,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080660,1083200}It is necessary.{NOTE:そこまで厳しくする必要があるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:04.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083200,1084750}We're not alone.{NOTE:あたしたちだけじゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:10.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084750,1090080}Both Fukuoka and Meihō's schools are just like us.{NOTE:福岡中学にしても、明本学園にしても、バレーを始めたものは皆そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:15.30,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090080,1095300}All of you chose volleyball, so own up to your decision.{NOTE:バレーを選んだからには、バレーに打ち込んでいくのが当然じゃないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:18.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095300,1098050}Practice for summer vacation will start at 8 o'clock every morning!{NOTE:夏休みの練習は毎朝八時に集合。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:22.97,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098050,1102970}Those who don't want to participate are free to quit, just like professor Hongou said.{NOTE:それが出来ない人は、本郷先生が言った通り、バレー部を止めてもらいより仕方ないわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:36.82,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115230,1116820}Kozue-kun.{NOTE:こずえくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:38.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116820,1118450}Oh? Ah, Tsutomu-kun.{NOTE:あ？あ、つとむくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:39.99,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118450,1119990}Yo. You still have training?{NOTE:よ。いままで練習会？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:41.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119990,1121570}Yeah, what about you?{NOTE:え。つとむくんも今まで？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:46.25,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121570,1126250}We still have meetings during the summer vacation. But it's nowhere near as difficult as your training.{NOTE:うん。夏休みの集会XXXね。でも、君たちほど大変じゃないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:48.21,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126250,1128210}I wonder about that.{NOTE:そうかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:02.68,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139380,1142680}Now that the gym is finished, you'll probably train every day, huh?{NOTE:体育館も出来さし、夏休みにずっと練習だね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:07.60,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142680,1147600}Seeing your practice, it's obvious that you'll win the autumn tournament.{NOTE:君たちの練習を見て、春と秋の連続優勝も間違いないって皆噂してるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:12.15,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149560,1152150}What's wrong? Are you tired from practice?{NOTE:どうしたんだ？練習で疲れてのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:16.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152150,1156900}No, that's not it. It's just that the girls say my training is too hard.{NOTE:んん。そうじゃないの。皆は練習が厳しすぎるって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:17.61,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156900,1157610}Huh?{NOTE:へ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:20.99,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157610,1160990}They don't want to practice every day during the summer.{NOTE:夏休みまで毎日練習することは(XXX・ないじゃない勝って言うのよ)。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:22.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160990,1162820}Even Midori and Kakko are against me.{NOTE:みどりやカッコまでよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:28.83,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162820,1168830}It's not like our opponents just sitting around during the spring. Everybody's stronger now.{NOTE:今度の大会のXXXは消して春のままじゃないのよ。皆新しい力を持って出てくるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168830,1170790}To keep up, we need to practice more.{NOTE:もっと、もっと練習しなきゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:33.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170790,1173630}And as their captain, I wanted to do my best.{NOTE:あたしはキャプテンとして一所懸命やってるつもりよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:36.09,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173630,1176090}I hoped that they would follow my spirit.{NOTE:皆も一緒にやってくれると思ってたのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:43.14,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181380,1183140}That alone is a difficult training.{NOTE:あれほど厳しい練習だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.39,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183140,1185390}Youth always wants to rebel.{NOTE:それは若い時に(XX・こっちもでるさ)。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:47.89,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185390,1187890}But it's the captain's role to pull the team together, right?{NOTE:それを引っ張って行くのはキャプテンの役目だろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:53.40,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189230,1193400}Sometimes a captain has to be hated by everyone. It's a lonely position.{NOTE:キャプテンって皆に憎まれなければ成らない。孤独な立場さ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:55.69,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193400,1195690}If not, then they won't be able to fulfill their role.{NOTE:又そうでなきゃ、役目を果たせないだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.69,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195690,1197690}Don't you agree?{NOTE:そうじゃないのかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:04.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203360,1204700}Yeah.{NOTE:そうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204700,1206240}You're right.{NOTE:そうなのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:17.09,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214960,1217090}All right, 8 o'clock. Assume positions.{NOTE:さ、八時よ。皆位置について。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:18.38,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1217090,1218380}Wah!{NOTE:わ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:20.17,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218380,1220170}Oyoshi, Ofuku, you're late.{NOTE:おヨシ。おフク。遅刻よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:22.17,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1220170,1222170}We're sorry.{NOTE:あ、ごめんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:25.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223760,1225430}All right. Let's start.{NOTE:さ、それじゃ行きましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:26.55,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1225430,1226550}Roger.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:51.58,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250080,1251580}I'm exhausted.{NOTE:厳しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:02.84,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260880,1262840}Naka!{NOTE:ナカ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:04.26,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262840,1264260}Captain, this is bad.{NOTE:参った、キャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:06.22,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264260,1266220}I can't move.{NOTE:もう動けないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:08.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266220,1268390}And yet you can move your mouth just fine.{NOTE:それだけ口を聞ける力があるじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:09.56,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268390,1269560}Come on.{NOTE:ほら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:12.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271310,1272520}Here goes.{NOTE:行くわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:18.98,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277980,1278980}Next!{NOTE:次！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:19.94,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278980,1279940}Okay.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:26.07,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285030,1286070}Are you okay?{NOTE:大丈夫？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:27.20,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286070,1287200}Somehow.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:29.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288120,1289780}Don't sleep.{NOTE:もっと取って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:36.25,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:1295160,1296250}Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:37.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296250,1297710}What's wrong?{NOTE:どうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:39.29,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297710,1299290}I hurt my knee.{NOTE:XXもいっちゃった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:41.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299290,1301050}A wound that small is nothing.{NOTE:そんな傷なんか何でもないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:42.51,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301050,1302510}You can still move, so you'll be fine.{NOTE:ほら、動けるX大丈夫よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:43.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302510,1303590}Get ready.{NOTE:行くわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:52.93,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1310930,1312930}What are you doing?{NOTE:ほら、なにしってんの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:54.27,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312930,1314270}Come on.{NOTE:ほら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:56.81,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314270,1316810}Stop it. Knock it off!{NOTE:止めて!もう止めて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:03.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321270,1323440}What is it, girls?{NOTE:どうしたのよ、皆？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.44,0:22:06.82,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323440,1326820}It's as you said. We can't accept 100 or even 50 balls, not if you throw them all at once.{NOTE:あなたの言うように、五十球も百球も一度には無理よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.82,0:22:08.66,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326820,1328660}Humans have their limits, you know!{NOTE:体力には限界があるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:11.74,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328660,1331740}There is a line between hard training and stupidity and you've crossed it.{NOTE:ハードトレーニングって無茶苦茶にやることは違うわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:13.41,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331740,1333410}So this training is stupidity?{NOTE:無茶苦茶だって言うの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:15.87,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333410,1335870}Yes, try to deny it all you want, but this is absurd.{NOTE:そうよ。いくらなんだって、これ以上無茶よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:17.58,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1335870,1337580}If you tried it, you'd get it.{NOTE:キャプテンだってやって見たら分かるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.58,0:22:19.75,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1337580,1339750}– Yeah. See for yourself.\N– Exactly.{NOTE:—そうよ。やって見れば分かるわよ。\\N—そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.75,0:22:21.71,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1339750,1341710}Okay then, let's do it.{NOTE:じゃ、やるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:25.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1342380,1345130}I'm ready. If I can do it, you can do it as well, right?{NOTE:さ、いいわよ。あたしができたら、皆もやるわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.13,0:22:26.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1345130,1346630}Very well.{NOTE:いいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.97,0:22:34.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1351970,1354450}I can do it even if I'm alone.{NOTE:さ、家のは一人で成っても、結構よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:35.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1354450,1355810}Strike all you can.{NOTE:どんどん打って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:22:56.58,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1375040,1376580}Here I go.{NOTE:行くわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:29.21,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:1407950,1409210}Knock it off!{NOTE:止めてよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.21,0:23:32.57,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:1409210,1412570}No matter what our captain does, ganging up on her is sick!{NOTE:いくらキャプテンだって四人じゃXX酷いわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:36.54,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1414700,1416540}Kozue!{NOTE:こずえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.54,0:23:42.37,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1420540,1422370}Are you finished?{NOTE:もうそれで終わりなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.37,0:23:46.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1422370,1426250}You still haven't reached 100 yet. So get on with it.{NOTE:まだ百球には成らないわ。さ、どんどん投げてちょうだい。}
