Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.76,0:23:54.14,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1431760,1434140}The district qualifiers for All-Japan championships begin.{NOTE:全国大会地区予選が始まった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.14,0:23:57.60,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1434140,1437600}With their eyes set on victory, Fujimi Academy passes the qualifier.{NOTE:連続優勝を狙う富士見学園は快調に勝ち進む。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.60,0:24:01.06,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1437600,1441060}But for some reason, Kudou's playing is particularly bad.{NOTE:だが、なぜか一人くどうの宮XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.06,0:24:03.94,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1441060,1443940}Coach Hongou leaves her in Kozue's care.{NOTE:本郷コーチは特訓をこずえに任せる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.94,0:24:07.78,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1443940,1447780}But then, in the middle of a special training, Kudou suddenly collapses.{NOTE:特訓は続く内に、くどうは突然崩れるように倒れる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.78,0:24:09.23,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1447780,1449230}Turns out, the special training is too much…{NOTE:ゆきすぎの特訓。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.23,0:24:11.65,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1449230,1451650}…and Kozue's frustration flares up again.{NOTE:こずえの不満が再び燃え上がった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.65,0:24:15.62,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1451650,1455620}Just then coach Hongou gives her a\hshocking order: "forfeit the title of captain".{NOTE:そして、本郷コーチまでが一度キャプテンを降りて(XX・見事)と言う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.62,0:24:19.33,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1455620,1459330}Please look forward to the next episode.{NOTE:さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}
